main event: An object resembling tracers, glowing white and red, was observed through field glasses for 50 minutes.
interesting points: The sighting occurred on September 16, 1955, at 0302 GMT., The object appeared to move at intervals in an 81x direction., The sighting was made by a civilian who used field glasses., The report concludes that the cause of the sighting was artillery firings from Fort Ord, California., No photographs were included in the document.
sighted object: glowing white and red object resembling tracers
